{"questionId":"14777","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>On her first day in a hospital, Kiri receives <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{u_1}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>u</mi>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> milligrams (mg) of a therapeutic drug. The amount of the drug Kiri receives increases by the same amount, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"d\">\n  <mi>d</mi>\n</math></span>, each day. On the seventh day, she receives 21 mg of the drug, and on the eleventh day she receives 29 mg.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Write down the value of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"d\">\n  <mi>d</mi>\n</math></span> and the value of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{u_1}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>u</mi>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>(<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{u_1}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>u</mi>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> =) 9&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><em>(A1)</em>(ft)</strong></p>\n<p>(<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"d\">\n  <mi>d</mi>\n</math></span> =)&nbsp;2&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><em>(A1)</em>(ft)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong>&nbsp;Follow through from part (a), but only if values are positive and&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{u_1}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>u</mi>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> &lt; 21.</p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"14777","referenceCode":"19M.2.SL.TZ2.T_4b","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Write down the value of d and the value of u 1 .","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.2—Arithmetic sequences and series","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.3—Geometric sequences and series","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.8—Use of technology to solve systems of linear equations and polynomial equations"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}